- if logged_in?
  - if session[:user]['headRef']
    %p
      Looks like you're fully certified!
  - elsif session[:user]['assRef'] and session[:user]['snitchRef']
    %p
      You've passed two of the tests, why not take a swing at the
      %a{href: '/tests?test=head'}
        Head Ref Test
  - else
    - if not session[:user]['assRef']
      %p
        The greatest journey begins with but a single step, or the 
        %a{href: '/tests?test=ass'}
          Assistant Ref Test
    - else
      %p
        You're a certified assistant ref!

    - if not session[:user]['snitchRef']
      %p
        Follow that tail! Take the 
        %a{href: '/tests?test=snitch'}
          Snitch Ref Test
    - else
      %p
        You're a certified snitch ref!